**Signs It's Hormonal:**
- Breakouts on jawline, chin, and lower face
- Flares around your period
- Deep, painful cysts (not surface pimples)
- Started or worsened after stopping birth control
- Accompanied by irregular periods, excess hair, or hair loss

**Common Hormonal Culprits:**
- PCOS (Polycystic Ovary Syndrome)
- Post-pill hormonal rebalancing
- Perimenopause
- Thyroid issues
- High cortisol (stress)
- Insulin resistance

