**Niacinamide**
- Reduces sebum production
- Anti-inflammatory
- Improves barrier
- 5-10% concentration

**Benzoyl Peroxide**
- Kills acne bacteria
- Short contact therapy (wash off after 10 min)
- Can bleach fabrics

**Salicylic Acid**
- Clears pores
- Anti-inflammatory
- 2% is standard

